name: Ip Man
description: Ip Man or Ip Kai Man (Chinese: ; pinyin: Yè Wèn) (1 October 1893 – 2 December 1972), better known as Great Master Ip Man was the first Chinese martial arts practice to teach Wing Chun openly. He had several students who later became independent martial arts teachers including Kwok Fu, Lun Kai, Ip Chun, Ip Ching, Leung Sheung and Bruce Lee.
